title: Learners Licence Confusion
selftext:
I m from Maharashtra and I applied for Learners License (LL) online through eKYC 
paid the 350inr fees and filled the form 

after that i watched the 12min road safety video
but after that when I try logging into LL test (STALL) I get a prompt saying " watch the video before proceeding" but on the verification page it shows that "you have watched the video"

very confused what to do

any help would be appreciated
thanks
